{{Quote|NO SHOES, NO SHIRT, NO EXTEE HELMET FILTERS<br />NO SERVICE<br />NO DROIDS ALLOWED.|sign in the window of the Poly Pyramid|<ref name="Lando Calrissian and the Mindharp of Sharu">''[[Lando Calrissian and the Mindharp of Sharu]]''</ref>}}
The '''Poly Pyramid''' was one of many inebriation emporiums in [[Teguta Lusat]] on [[Rafa IV]]. It was visited mostly by [[Mining/Legends|miners]] and once by [[Lando Calrissian/Legends|Lando Calrissian]] in [[4 BBY/Legends|4 BBY]]. Lando's [[Droid/Legends|droid]] companion at the [[Time/Legends|time]], [[Vuffi Raa]], had to wait outside because droids were not allowed inside. It had a bar running down the left side of the building with booths lining the opposite wall. On the walls hung paintings and scenes from sporting events from around [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]].

